flowchart TD
    A[Trained MDT + input instance x] --> B[Compute original prediction y]
    B --> C[Enumerate opposite-class paths]
    C --> D[Initialize selected feature set S\n(typically all features)]
    D --> E[Run weak_axp_check(S)]
    E --> F{Deletion loop over feature f}
    F --> G[Try S' = S \\ {f}]
    G --> H{weak_axp_check(S') true?}
    H -- Yes --> I[Remove f from S]
    H -- No --> J[Keep f in S]
    I --> F
    J --> F
    F --> K[Subset-minimal weak AXp]
    K --> L[Note: subset-minimal != cardinality-minimal]
